==Latin==

===Alternative forms===
* [[res]] audita perit, litera scripta manet: A thing heard perishes; the written letter remains.
* litera scripta manet, [[verbum]] [[ut]] [[inane]] perit: The written letter remains, as the empty word perishes.
* [[littera]] scripta manet, [[volat]] [[irrevocabile]] verbum: The written letter remains, the spoken word flies away, not to be recalled.
* vox [[emissa]] volat, litera scripta manet: While words spoken may fly away, the written letter remains.
* [[verba]] volant, scripta manent: The words fly away, the written letter remains.

